{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Describing an App’s structure and mechanics is a good way to scope out and understand what to build."}]},{"anchor":"App-Behavior","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"App Behavior"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"What does the app do?"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Plays movies and TV episodes."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Keeps track of what your are watching."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Searches a library of content."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Allows you to manually add content to your own list."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Signs in and out of an account."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Organizes content in various forms (featured, popular, trending)"}]}]}]},{"anchor":"App-Anatomy","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"App Anatomy"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The apps screens and components are described below."}]},{"anchor":"Overall-Look-and-Feel","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Overall Look and Feel"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The app has a highly customized look and feel, themed with a custom color scheme. Buttons have a branded appearance, all screens have a custom background. Lots of rich imagery is loaded remotely on all screens."}]},{"anchor":"Tab-Bar","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Tab Bar"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The app has 3 tabs:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Home - The latest content, continue watching, for you, my list, just added, popular movies, popilar TV, and other trending content."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Search - Find what youre looking for with text search, explore collections, and popular searches."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Account - A place to switch profiles, see your list of content, and continue watching."}]}]}]},{"anchor":"The-Side-Bar","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"The Side Bar"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The HBO app has a sidebar that animates in from the left and is dismisses by tapping an X. It occupies around 90% of the screen width on an iPhone."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The content of the sidebar is a scrolling list of items, in multiple sections."}]},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The first section is various zones of the app featuring different kinds of content."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The second section is categories."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The third section is audio description content."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The fourth section is HBO channels (e.g. HBO, Cinemax, Adult Swim)"}]}]}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"App Zones"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Series"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Movies"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Originals"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Just Added"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Last Chance"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Coming Soon"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Trending Now"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Awards and Aclaim"}]}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Categories"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Action"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Animation"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Comedy"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Crime"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Documentaries"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Drama"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Fantasy & Sci-Fi"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Horror"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"International"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Kids & Family"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Latino"}]}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Audio Description"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Channels"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"HBO"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Max Originals"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"DC"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TCM"}]}]}]}]}]},{"anchor":"TV-Show-Details-Screen","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"TV Show - Details Screen"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When tapping on a TV show additional details are shown:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A thumbnail of the content bleeding under the navigation bar."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A play button."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Button to add to your list."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Button to play a trailer."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Button to download."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Title and Description."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A seasons area listing the episodes."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Each episode has a thumbnnail title, duration, rating and download button."}]}]}]},{"anchor":"TV-Show-Episode-Screen","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"TV Show - Episode Screen"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Similar to the TV Show Details Screen, this screen shows:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A thumbnail of the content bleeding under the navigation bar."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A play button."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Button to add to your list."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Button to play a trailer."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An extras section with a horizontal carousel of additional content."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Collapsable headers for Cast and Crew, Producers, Directors, Writers, Rating each with a 50-50 layout."}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Movie-Details-Screen","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Movie - Details Screen"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When tapping on a Movie additional details are shown:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A thumbnail of the content bleeding under the navigation bar."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A play button."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Button to add to your list."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Button to play a trailer."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Button to download."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Title and Description."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A “more like this” section with a horizontal carousel of other movies. Each movie shows a thumbnail without title or additional information. A small lable shows the channel (HBO, Cinemax)."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Collapsable headers for Cast and Crew, Producers, Directors, Writers, Rating each with a 50-50 layout."}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Home-Screen","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Home Screen"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Multiple horizontal carousels with different aspect ratios."}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Movies have a 2\/3 vertical rectangle."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Episodes may have a 4\/3 horizontal rectangle."}]}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Some areas are a single large header with a button for more info."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“Hubs” show extra large rectangular content and link to the channels areas in the sidebar above."}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Search-Screen","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Search Screen"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A search bar in the navigation area."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A horizontal scrolling carousel of collections to explore."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Popular searches: A 2x2 grid of movies and TV shows with 2\/3 vertical rectangular thumbnails."}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Progress-Bar","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Progress Bar"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A small progress bar may appear on multiple elements showing the overall viewing status of a movie or TV show."}]},{"anchor":"Playback-Screen","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Playback Screen"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A rewind 15s button."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A fast forward 15s button."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An airplay button."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A captions button."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A scrubber to navigate."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A channel logo with a title."}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Planning-the-Build","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Planning the Build"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"How would we go about building this? Do we use UIKit? Do we use SwiftUI? Both?"}]},{"anchor":"Use-Cases-for-UIKit","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Use Cases for UIKit"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This app has a lot of grids. Some scrolling horizontally, others vertically. It is a strong use case for UICollectionView and UICollectionViewCompositionalLayout."}]},{"anchor":"Use-Cases-for-SwiftUI","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Use Cases for SwiftUI"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This app has a lot of grids. It is a strong use case for using ScrollViews with LazyVGrids and LazyHGrids. There is also a lot of appearance customization that SwiftUI might be better at than UIKit."}]},{"anchor":"Data-Storage","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Data Storage"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The app loads JSON from a server to show its content. Storing data locally could occur with a variety of technologies:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"User Defaults"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Core Data"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Realm or some other third party library."}]}]}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":2,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/jylearningblueprint\/making-an-hbo-clone"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/JYLearningBlueprint\/documentation\/JYLearningBlueprint\/Making-an-HBO-Clone","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A clone of the HBO app for iOS. For eductational purposes only. The HBO app is a fantasitic app with rich content, unique UI, and a lot of custom appearance work. I wanted to learn a lot, so I cloned it."}],"kind":"article","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Making an HBO Clone","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"JYLearningBlueprint"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/JYLearningBlueprint\/documentation\/JYLearningBlueprint"]]},"references":{"doc://JYLearningBlueprint/documentation/JYLearningBlueprint":{"role":"collection","title":"JYLearningBlueprint","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A collection of everything I’ve learned as an iOS Developer."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/JYLearningBlueprint\/documentation\/JYLearningBlueprint","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/jylearningblueprint"}}}